ICS 10 Course Reference<h1>How Computers Work</h1>
<P>
  <B>Instructor:</B>  <A HREF="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~kay/">David G. Kay</A>,
  5056 Donald Bren Hall
(<code><A HREF="mailto:kay@uci.edu">kay@uci.edu</A></code>). TA: <!-- <A HREF="https://sites.google.com/site/cdwheelock/"> -->Harun Anver<!--</A>--> (<code><A HREF="mailto:hanver@uci.edu">hanver@uci.edu</A></code>).  Reader: Swadhyaya Kumar. Special assistants: <a href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~djr/DebraJRichardson/Home.html">Debra Richardson</a> and <a href="http://faculty.sites.uci.edu/aregan/">Amelia Regan</a>.</P>
<P><B>Quick links: </B>  
<a href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~kay/courses/10/hw/index.html">Assignments</a> <a href="http://ics-10-partner-app.appspot.com">Partner App </a><a href="http://www.bitsbook.com"><i>Blown to Bits</i> book</a>
